# Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# NEVER commit .env to version control

# ===========================================
# INSTRUCTIONS
# ===========================================
# This file shows the structure of required environment variables
# but contains NO actual secret values.
#
# For development:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your actual keys in .env
# 3. .env is gitignored and will not be committed
#
# For production:
# Use the Configuration panel in the app (owner-only access)
# to securely store secrets in Spark KV storage.
# ===========================================

